41-939e-5b6ef6ec2084","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"013e695a-735f-4fc2-a81e-3391c6bb25cc","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["It takes a while to break in the Philips Saeco Intuita, but once you’ve learned your machine and pulled several shots through it, the flavor of espresso gets better and better. Although this espresso maker may take more time and effort to maintain than other machines, it has several convenient features to help remind you to take care of it."]},"id":"8eef0876-8e2e-4e76-9b13-a39a3176a128","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_67391","url":"/philips-saeco-intuita-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"linda-thomson","url":"/author/linda-thomson","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Linda Thomson","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"SD7AJ8PTDFstvquABQDpsH","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-11-04T17:35:40Z","datePublished":"2015-11-04T17:35:40Z","name":"Philips Saeco Intuita HD8750/47","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it is no longer available.","review":{"rating":88,"verdict":"The Philips Saeco Intuita brews up to two shots of espresso in a single go, which means you can quickly create espresso shots for everyone who wants one &#8211; or two. This machine requires more maintenance than others we tested, though. ","pros":["This machine makes consistently excellent espresso."],"cons":["You have to perform more maintenance with this machine than most of the espresso makers in our lineup."]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it is no longer available.","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-11-04T17:35:40Z","id":"m2fKpCzBMFjUpe5ypaJGqK","meta":{"title":"Philips Saeco Intuita HD8750/47 Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"A super automatic espresso machine like the Philips Saeco Int